s="core-article-notes"><h4>Notes</h4><div role="paragraph">Various cardiovascular and pulmonary complications of liver cirrhosis are reviewed, and their imaging features are described and illustrated.</div></section></section><section id="tab-contributors" role="tabpanel"><h3>Authors</h3><section class="core-authors"><h4>Affiliations</h4><div id="con1" property="author" typeof="Person"><div class="heading"><span property="givenName">Yoon Kyung</span> <span property="familyName">Kim</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></div><div class="content"><div class="affiliations"><div property="affiliation" typeof="Organization"><span property="name">From the Department of Radiology, School of Medicine, Ewha Womans University, 911-1 Mokdong Yangcheon-gu, Seoul 158-710, Korea (Y.K.K., Y.K., S.S.S.); and the Department of Radiology, Korea University Guro Hospital, Seoul, Korea (Y.K.K.). Presented as an education exhibit at the 2007 RSNA Annual Meeting. Received April 11, 2008; revision requested July 25 and received September 12; accepted September 15. All authors have no financial relationships to disclose.</span></div></div><div class="core-author-link"><a href="/authored-by/Kim/Yoon+Kyung" rel="nofollow">View all articles by this author</a></div></div></div><div id="con2" property="author" typeof="Person"><div class="heading"><span property="givenName">Yookyung</span> <span property="familyName">Kim</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></div><div class="content"><div class="affiliations"><div property="affiliation" typeof="Organization"><span property="name">From the Department of Radiology, School of Medicine, Ewha Womans University, 911-1 Mokdong Yangcheon-gu, Seoul 158-710, Korea (Y.K.K., Y.K., S.S.S.); and the Department of Radiology, Korea University Guro Hospital, Seoul, Korea (Y.K.K.). Presented as an education exhibit at the 2007 RSNA Annual Meeting. Received April 11, 2008; revision requested July 25 and received September 12; accepted Sept